     <div type="encomium">
   <head>❧ To the Authour.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>THine Art and Subiect both such Worth containe,</l>
      <l>That thou art best requited in thy paine.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>EDVV. HERBRET <hi>Knight.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
